<headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 05 at 5:46AM EDT  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...Patchy dense fog for the the morning commute...
Motorists will likely encounter rapidly changing visibilities
this morning, possibly as low as one quarter mile or less,
generally along and north of Route 6. If you encounter dense fog,
slow down, make sure to use low beam headlights and use caution at
intersections.</description>
